{"tid":756930,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"贏國鄭州「明星橋」偷步通車4個月 爆裂露鋼板全座急維修","createTime":"2018-07-26T11:43:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-26T12:12:36.000Z","uid":136994,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"e1f0b28f4fa9cbcb886117415a2ecac9472fb35f","tid":756930,"uid":136994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T11:43:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180726&amp;s=10793096&amp;a=58485569\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180726%26s%3D10793096%26a%3D58485569&d=XOSbgD3UyiEruwmKbaO1DdU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=ebe6e344\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180726%26s%3D10793096%26a%3D58485569&h=ce0cbf28\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180726&amp;s=10793096&amp;a=58485569</a>  <br />\n<br />\n（新增：內容）造價超過1億元人民幣（約1.18億港元）、耗時近3年的河南鄭州中牟縣的賈魯河大橋，堪稱全亞洲最闊的無背索斜塔斜拉結構橋，一度被稱為鄭州新地標！這條「明星橋」今年3月下旬疑偷步通車，剛使用了4個月，近日爆出橋面就出現大量破損和裂縫，甚至能清晰看到碎石下面的鋼板，需要全座橋重新翻修。網民批評是「豆腐渣工程」，內媒則認為未驗收就通車，無疑是「豆腐渣管理」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n賈魯河大橋的承建商表示，大橋路面破損的原因已經找到，正在進行維修，橋樑質量安全不受任何影響。專家一致認為，鋼橋面鋪裝對溫度變化非常敏感，因晝夜溫差較大，正交異性的鋼橋面板柔韌度大，產生溫差變形。目前，大橋西半幅道路正在整修，預計9月1日完成。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180725/large/1532522329_c28c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180725%2Flarge%2F1532522329_c28c.jpg&h=92ae6fdb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d74ccbfef234f306788a2e3ecfb05d0847a7502e","tid":756930,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T11:48:10.000Z","msg":"因晝夜溫差較大，<span style=\"color: red;\">正交異性</span>的鋼橋面板柔韌度大<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7d8c5c90da436fa20a45ea62cf9656b77c7e23b","tid":756930,"uid":53524,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T11:51:44.000Z","msg":"1億<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 都未見過大蛇柯尿"},{"pid":"f215133110dc27e21c1c744b0d4784f57ca73a60","tid":756930,"uid":132587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T11:51:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/06/173932_3fb5ed13afe8714a7e5d13ee506003dd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F06%2F173932_3fb5ed13afe8714a7e5d13ee506003dd.jpg&h=cfbdb209&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日中國 聽日香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b69ce11f118eeb74d9480be9f1b154d692f49428","tid":756930,"uid":75326,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T11:55:06.000Z","msg":"元朗條橋幾錢?"},{"pid":"43d5bab30a7403ad82ae0c0423adbd3b3a22c979","tid":756930,"uid":110019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T11:58:42.000Z","msg":"就算無偷工減料同貪污，一億建造費會唔會平得滯呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49fc3ec8f1a1f1fa970085d4a6dd6b0925efc873","tid":756930,"uid":66119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T11:58:49.000Z","msg":"與中國接軌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddb18353b7c0dcbdbc0971dd5ebd3da85b06c8e9","tid":756930,"uid":11809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T12:00:42.000Z","msg":"右邊果條直頭mei咗"},{"pid":"46527cecc870dd91ca263547a35ec4ad38919800","tid":756930,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T12:12:36.000Z","msg":"wfc 又唔會去"}]}